title: NBC Special - Remembering Tim Russert - 2008-06-13
description:
TV Show: Remembering Tim Russert
Episode: Self-Titled NBC Special
Air Date: Friday, June 13, 2008
Network: NBC
File Note: Listed as 2008-06-14, but correct to 2008-06-13

NOTE: This is not the same episode of Sunday&#039;s Meet The Press. This show was a last minute episode announced Friday, and aired later that evening at 10PM Eastern-Pacific.

A one-hour episode dedicated to NBC&#039;s Washington Bureau Chief and 17-year Moderator Tim Russert.

This episode is hosted by NBC News veteran, Tom Brokaw.

Tim Russert: May 7, 1950 - June 13, 2008
